Interface ControlInterface

All Known Subinterfaces:
CheckBoxInterface, ComboBoxInterface, DataGridInterface, DatePickerInterface, ListBoxInterface, RadioButtonInterface, TextAreaInterface, TextFieldInterface
All Known Implementing Classes:
CheckBox, ComboBox, Control, DataGrid, DatePicker, ListBox, RadioButton, TextArea, TextField
public interface ControlInterface

This interface stores necessary informations about the control that gets added to the Container on dynamically generated User Interface.

Author:
